賤民20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未來還未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n短暫的婚姻之後又等咗半年比王貽興我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18年提都廢事提<br />\n<br />\n2019年<br />\n以婚內情教束理想國假設性無罪<del>黑市</del>形成小陽春<br />\n二月廿九為高潮<br />\n<br />\n然後又轉返韓劇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c2dde34bfbe62001420e7e54af4ffbc9e874a0","tid":1961223,"uid":30506,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"冇人講咪你講囉我屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講唔撚得架？好撚委屈你架？其他人開post講撚咗先我係咪又可以屌你唔撚講先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪覺得冇人講，自己就好撚有優越感，開post就係都要加多一兩句屌人先得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚嘢話題都實有第一個人講架啦，係咪個撚個開post都要屌人「ＸＸ都冇人講」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好聲好氣唔撚得嘅，係咪以為個撚個都廿四小時mon撚住乜柒都知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲戇鳩仔，完全喺到消磨所有人嘅耐性，助長負面情緒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母我真係唔撚知有件咁嘅事啊嘛，碌碌下post無撚啦啦畀你屌，唔撚知唔撚得架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人知冇人提咁咪你提話人知囉我屌你老母，你知又唔撚講其他人唔知又可以點撚樣講啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接收資訊嗰個一定要畀發放資訊嗰個屌架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪你細個你老竇教你寫字嗰陣一路教一路屌你老母先教到你呢啲撚樣出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母臭閪谷鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3c611f12e831813920c441d6b02268698b6580","tid":1961223,"uid":272119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"睇住yoshi 過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec01ecb805d0289cbfb7417f93fc39971eb7a4d","tid":1961223,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"點解viutv仲播警訊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1912802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1912802</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/epg/99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fepg%2F99&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=c322df9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/epg/99</a><br />\n節目表Ch. 99<br />\n<br />\n10星期五<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6:30<br />\n警訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第133集</span><br />\n<br />\n2020年3月4日<br />\n【Now新聞台】<br />\n根據免費電視牌照條件，現時ViuTV每周在中文頻道播放2.5小時港台節目，包括《警訊》、《看見溫度》。ViuTV表示，對通訊局的決定表示歡迎，在編排節目上更具彈性。<br />\n<br />\n彈完仲播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85cb939f82a7150176d56f42474ca3f87e36833","tid":1961223,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:49:10.000Z","msg":"Happy birthday"},{"pid":"789dddc2cf6be3bd38a8811a0e9185147d6b2198","tid":1961223,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"viu最高收視：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/viutv-03_qTlpz_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fviutv-03_qTlpz_1200x0.png&h=4ab99edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>世界盃冠軍戰法國對克羅地亞，ViuTV昨晚11時直播法國對克羅地亞的決賽，收視創下ViuTV開台以來最高紀錄。ViuTV公布，昨晚決賽時段，ViuTV錄得平均收視24.4點，最高更加有26.6點（約177萬人次），創下ViuTV開台以來的平均和最高收視紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n另外，網絡平台串流收播率高達41萬次。<br />\n<br />\n據蘋果日報報道，無綫昨晚9點至11點半播出電影《使徒行者》應戰，平均 15點（98萬人次）；11點半《晚間新聞》平均4點（26萬人次）；11時50分至凌晨2點的兩集《刑事偵緝檔案IV》只得2點（13萬人次）。</em>"},{"pid":"4b6dbbac191cf18f8b5f86c2b6580d9d652a6b6b","tid":1961223,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"其實最早計「綜合收視」加埋網上點擊嘅係viutv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過論造數始祖梗係五五開亞視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99b72c4a4672d3edaab3bdc537c7b9cc0c4ea2e","tid":1961223,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"趁cctvb出機場黑警就咪撚8半播韓劇啦"},{"pid":"c0c5cc8c83381d71a512b78fefd2d185f4b5b2fa","tid":1961223,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"2018年，無綫電視、ViuTV、奇妙電視聯同香港11間廣告商會成員公司成立「香港電視觀眾收視調查創辦委員會」（FSC），並委任中國廣視索福瑞媒介研究（CSM）為2018年至2023年的香港電視觀眾收視調查機構。新監測方式則會分成「家中電視觀看」（In-home TV Viewing）及「網上觀看」（Online Viewing）兩種。前者將目標抽樣家庭由 800 個增加至 1,000 個，即是在該 1,000 個樣本家庭中安裝「個人收視記錄儀」，並監測每個家庭的樣本成員所觀看的內容，包括免費電視或收視電視節目，以至各種外接至電視的訊源如衛星電視、串流影視內容、影碟、遊戲機等，而收集的數據將會包括直播、時間平移（Time Shift）以及 7 天內的點播重溫內容。另外，加入「網上觀看」（Online Viewing）數據。「網上觀看」收視數據將會分為 3 部分，包括由 comScore 提供的「串流標籤」（Streaming Tag）統計數據、「家庭互聯網測量儀」（Focal Meter）及「虛擬測量儀」（Virtual Meter），去監測所有在線裝置觀看電視節目的情況。所謂「串流標籤」，就是用作監測指定裝置觀看相關網站及 Apps 的內容種類、觀看時間等使用情況；而「家庭互聯網測量儀」則是監測家中所有在線裝置，去確定裝置是否在家中觀看節目；至於「虛擬測量儀」則是用作記錄那一位家庭成員正在使用某一裝置。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">大家都係同一個玩法<br />\n不過viu 同奇妙冇公開咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0534185024e8dff8ca38785627f4a93fda357837","tid":1961223,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"Viutv生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家日日都睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97edd47054d44fde6eacf3fb719ae63a207aeb3","tid":1961223,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl